==============================================================================
** Source Code: **
==============================================================================
Full Source Code can be found under: <https://code.google.com/p/project-qpl/>.
Currently it uses SVN (Subversion).
You need to have Subversion installed on your system to check out a copy of
the source code.
Use this command to get the latest sources:
'$ svn  checkout  http://project-qpl.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/  qpl'
 

